Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:34.99,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,While the show was on a one year break,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:40.09,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, Kagura-chan, and everyone else I knew changed into completely different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:44.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And they all claimed that two years had passed since the show went off the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.58,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Wartirine / Warti / Wartise]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.52,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to escape this cruel reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and arrived at the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:51.07,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,only to find a very different Kyubei-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:53.88,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And there was more to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.71,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Sir Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.39,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:06.42,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,...became Zurako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:12.02,Default,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Everyone Looks Pretty Grown Up After Summer Break]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Your characters don't overlap at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:17.07,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You stinkin' lunatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.82,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who's stupid enough to have his balls removed to avoid character overlap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.27,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And hell, you're both trannies now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:26.88,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,C-Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:30.37,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,I was so focused on the details that I lost sight of the big picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.83,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all you lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.02,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kyubei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:38.94,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that we are doomed to share the same character traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:43.05,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,One of us must be eliminated for the sake of more screen time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.06,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,One has both balls and boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.33,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,The other has neither balls nor boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:51.24,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Let us determine who the true transsexual is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:53.81,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,The position of gay bar champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.34,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...shall be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:59.08,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even worth fighting over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.49,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:05.48,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,First people growing, now people changing their gender...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:08.00,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that hasn't changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.83,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...is how they're still a bunch of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.00,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:18.09,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Shinsengumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.52,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Stinkin' four eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:18.48,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,You got guts to escape from your first day on the job, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:21.39,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,You're ready to die, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.11,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:29.61,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That bazooka is Okita-san's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.60,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babblin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.80,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see you for a while, and you need glasses for your brain now, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.36,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.77,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Commander of the Shinsengumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.07,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy Yamazaki, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.80,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Now move your ass, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.04,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.75,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Average Joe Yamazaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.95,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,That's ancient history!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.40,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I was still a cherry boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.88,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I stand fully erect now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:03.17,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jimmy Yamazaki, the vice-commander who makes crying babies cry harder, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.18,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.95,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.92,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're addicted to anpan now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:11.03,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's even showing up in your speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.95,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, start driving, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:13.60,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.86,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I said to drive the damn car, nitwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.03,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:21.99,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanted to say hello first since it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.91,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's gonna remember a no name like you, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.41,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long, Shinpachi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.84,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Toshiro Hijikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.12,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.33,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-Hijikata-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.81,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Hijikata-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:36.63,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san would never smile like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Especially not after being slapped around by someone like Yamazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:45.51,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that supposed to mean? Explain, Hijikata, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.11,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He's smiling after being hit for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.35,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,A lot's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:55.13,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I took over as commander after Kondo-san retired,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:59.60,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,but it became painfully clear that ruling through fear would no longer work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:05.12,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,And after some thinking, I decided to halve my way of life, my mayonnaise intake, and my calorie intake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:09.70,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, I'm now known as Toshi-san, the Shinsengumi's collective bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You ended up losing your position in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.26,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I never thought I'd have the opportunity to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.31,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's making me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.37,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please stop being so creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:21.03,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,How are Gin-san and Kagura-chan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.52,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,They should have tagged along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:25.51,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,It's been pretty lonely without Kondo-san around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.93,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.18,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How can you call yourself Hijikata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:31.51,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.14,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinsengumi has seen a complete overhaul...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.24,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.02,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Shinsengumi Station]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinsengumi Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:50.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Seig heil, Herr Okita de Sade Sogo III!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.02,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.71,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.86,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:02.57,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He's been promoted way past the rank of commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.43,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.46,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Two years have passed since the formation of the Holy Shinsengumi Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.40,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Empire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.60,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This is an empire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:15.46,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your efforts, the empire has been able to extend its influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:18.78,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,We now control over half of Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.22,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't sound like the police anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:26.10,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before the day comes when we slaughter the Shogun and hoist the flag of our empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.59,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,...over Edo Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.18,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That would make you Joi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.89,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That would make you terrorists now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:36.35,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,However, we must first take control of a certain area before we can begin our crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.79,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,An impregnable town of steel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.83,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,A lawless place for the ruffians of Edo to gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.18,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,The Kabuki district!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.84,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Kabuki District 1st Street]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.84,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't secure this town before launching our attack on Edo Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.76,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,it will come back to haunt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.07,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,But worry not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:53.15,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Every stronghold has a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.88,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,And I now have the means to exploit that weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.04,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,We have taken a friend of Shogun Sakata, the fearless general of the Kabuki district...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.57,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,...as a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:05.02,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,The town of steel will fall quickly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.45,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.47,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this fearless general?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.72,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to crush Odd Jobs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:14.16,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,I will eliminate anyone who stands in the way of my ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.19,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Your ambition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:18.89,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,When did you join the camp of cliche Edo dominating megalomaniacs, Jerkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.93,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.99,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, you should address me as Jerk of a Kaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.75,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,I get annoyed when people combine words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:30.63,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I would have you executed, but I'll spare your life since you have use as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.02,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata, take him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.04,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Jerkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.35,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Yamazaki, smack him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.83,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Jerkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.57,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this catching on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.17,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, execute everyone besides the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.35,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Jerkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.35,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.41,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, I'll change my title to Jerkaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.27,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,But make the "Jer" inaudible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.75,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.47,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.32,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.34,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.75,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody I know is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.54,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Stop sniffling, you wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.08,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found someone normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.27,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't look like you'll be much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.73,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-Hijikata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.51,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:17.32,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I was also left behind two years, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.90,Default,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,Here is this week's spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:35.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This week's spotlight came in third on the sales chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:41.01,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The third single from singer-songwriter MADAO-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Cardboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.30,Default,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.79,Default,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,Another top-seller?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.21,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Beer is Best]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.55,Default,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you cut your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.93,Default,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I grew it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:53.66,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,MADAO-san got the inspiration for this song from the sound of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:09:01.06,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[How MADAO got his break]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:09:01.06,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Reenactment]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tearing apart cardboard when he was living on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:09:01.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,He performed many concerts on the street before achieving his current popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.78,Default,Tamo,0000,0000,0000,,So how does it feel to go from living on the streets to cutting your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:05.86,Default,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I didn't cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.12,Default,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,I grew it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:10.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we're running out of time, so please get on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.87,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here's MADAO-san with "I Cut My Hair."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.78,Default,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,I said I didn't cut my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.07,Default,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to cut my hair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.64,Default,Madao,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look bad with long hair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:21.31,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:25.24,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I went back to the station after the one year break, and everything was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.58,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,As though everyone else had spent the past two years without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.81,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.02,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you pretend to be different?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:37.07,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Because I thought that I was the one who was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.50,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.94,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Every other person had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.50,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I was the exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:47.25,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Given the situation, what else could I do but laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.77,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Please wait one moment.]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.62,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I couldn't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:53.19,Default,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you, Hijikata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.34,Default,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're gonna get away with this, an?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.37,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.60,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Did we travel through time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:08.08,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones stuck in a completely different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:12.12,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.09,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're being punished...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.41,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:21.00,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.62,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...slacking off on playing the straight man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:28.87,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I was always exhausted after dealing with the onslaught of funny men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.13,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all the work, I wasn't very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.69,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And there wasn't much merchandise featuring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:36.88,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I had to wonder if playing a funny man paid better dividends...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:40.40,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So while they were airing reruns for the past year,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:40.41,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Yorinuki Gintama-san]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:44.08,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I kicked back and completely forgot about playing the straight man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:44.03,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Otsuu Plus]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:49.08,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But while I was doing nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:52.46,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,everyone else found something to do and build on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.25,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They were moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.51,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:02.22,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing that you know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.69,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You were the only normal person in the Shinsengumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.02,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You were also in the straight man position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.93,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But then you added that funny man persona, Tosshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.35,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That was because of the sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:15.22,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...and engaged in bizarre behavior involving mayonnaise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.20,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I just happen to like mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.54,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Then how do you explain the smiling act?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:22.63,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanted to play a funny man, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.85,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.38,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you honestly say that you weren't trying to enjoy yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:30.35,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I said enough already, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.62,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.88,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I shouldn't have snapped at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.99,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.32,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,If the world was twisted into its current state by an oversaturation of funny men
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:45.23,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,because the two of us stopped playing straight men,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:50.14,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have any right to gripe about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:52.83,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:58.62,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.06,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.52,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.82,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,...to the Holy Shinsengumi Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.91,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to stop the kaiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.94,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,...from attacking Odd Jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.83,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to help anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.72,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:20.54,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on working at Odd Jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.56,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san may look like Yamcha
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and Kagura may be bigger than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.58,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but Odd Jobs is still the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.69,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck playing the straight man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:29.94,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:35.60,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it's going to change anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:41.06,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have a breaking news update.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:45.38,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious wart outbreak is continuing to spread throughout Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:49.26,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Medical scientists have finally determined the source of this malady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.96,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,The warts, which attach themselves to organisms and absorb their life energy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:56.06,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,before eventually taking over the host body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:13:00.71,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,have been identified as parasitic aliens known as Q'Sai Nettles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.44,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,First, the aliens transform into the figure on your left
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.64,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,and assimilate information from the host.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.11,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, it transforms into something completely identical to the host.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.46,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,The alien supplants the host
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:15.15,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,and matures the appearance of the host by two years after a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:20.23,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,It should be noted that these aliens are attracted to ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.53,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,People with more ambition have a higher chance of being infected,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.59,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,and the aliens will evolve according to that ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:31.69,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anyone who's gone through a sudden change and talked about two years passing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.70,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that they've been infected by Q'Sai Nettles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.56,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,First, you should check if the comatose original is hanging from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.74,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Then use something like a paper fan to smack the Q'Sai Nettle as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.80,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends have not changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.93,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Two years haven't passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.51,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,The world before you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.61,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,...a world with warts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.89,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Kusano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.68,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,There's something hanging from your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.44,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.06,Default,Kusano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.18,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:03.82,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.29,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.37,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,They're all Wartiharu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.90,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Yamcha Gin-san is just a Yamcha wart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.58,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The grown-up Kagura-chan is just a wart with two big warts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.83,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The gorilla couple is two warts making a wart baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.84,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Ambition, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.53,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:25.73,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't infected because we were slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:30.50,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we're the only ones who can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:34.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I know exactly what I need to do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.50,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna paper fan this twisted wartiworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:40.19,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And take back our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.15,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.58,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.54,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking everywhere for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.44,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Kagura-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:50.50,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.07,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:52.72,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.31,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Smack her with the fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.05,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the wart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.12,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Kagura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:02.13,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair to press that body up against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.43,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I was so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:09.59,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,An Odd Jobs without you is like you without glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.23,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean you only need my glasses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.59,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.95,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really a wart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.05,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This cute girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.90,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, does it even matter if she's a wart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.73,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:33.29,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiser Okita de Sade Sogo III!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.08,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-Hijikata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:40.19,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see you hit a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.42,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.40,Default,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Jerkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.08,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.26,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,A-After Kondo-san left,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:52.11,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,I devoted my life to making the force bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:59.11,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hesitate to commit atrocities for the sake of protecting the Shinsengumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.48,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,But Hijikata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.56,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,If I let you get your hands dirty,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:08.19,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,the Shinsengumi will just be a gang of thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.42,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:10.71,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.46,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wart! Just a wart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:15.05,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:19.28,Default,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,...to have another bowl of mayonnaise with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.43,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.90,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You said it was dog food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.21,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.92,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Sogo! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.24,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's not going to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.45,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who needs to get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.21,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we establish that he's just a wart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.35,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.55,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.13,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.80,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,A samurai would never attack a dying man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.07,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.72,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,And she already gave birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.80,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,How could you be so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.68,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to tell this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:47.19,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.52,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,She's not your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.39,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a wart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.43,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.83,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:56.49,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you use my sister's face to play wife to the gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.50,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.64,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.41,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.34,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,The father of my child is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.17,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:07.65,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.00,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.91,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,That V-shaped hair is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:11.95,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.63,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How could the two of you have a kid when you barely even know each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.97,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Toshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.69,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hide my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:22.52,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Even after pretending to be married to Isao-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.45,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.27,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's turned into one hell of a slutty bitch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.31,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.32,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Take us away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.30,Default,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,To a world without gorillas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.15,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.30,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.34,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.47,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you could fool me with such a cheap trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.53,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the kid and scram.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:42.80,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.54,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've been completely fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.97,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you spare the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:49.68,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Let me raise Togoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:50.48,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.09,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is Togoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.80,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? His name is Togoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.15,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,What an adorable child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.51,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind letting me hold him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.81,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's a newborn, so you'll need to support his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:06.50,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,My, such an adorable child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.19,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,His mother and father must be lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.83,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not as adorable as my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:13.19,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.31,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Isako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.55,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.52,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.48,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've completely lost your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.16,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have your happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:22.83,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,You're all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.05,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,You're all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:27.13,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,...headed straight down misery lane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.24,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,T-Togoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.80,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer be a straight man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.29,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've been completely fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.06,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:36.66,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll jump off with the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:37.74,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Kondo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.62,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not be hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.97,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who needs to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.60,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be smacking down warts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.79,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stopping a wart from killing itself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.41,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,The child has done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.61,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You should blame...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:47.76,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,...Otae and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.75,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Blame your poor excuse for a brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.39,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.98,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:53.95,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Spare Togoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.69,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you giving up your life for a wart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.99,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,To protect your child with your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:02.49,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't thats how a true parent would behave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.49,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Yet look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:08.50,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to die by yourself and leave us behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:10.87,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.88,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:19.75,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember who comforted you at the bar after your wife ran out on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.14,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.16,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,From the bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.68,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,From the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.88,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Zurako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.13,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.30,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How did you give birth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.69,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You are a father now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:35.12,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,So for her sake, for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.11,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You must live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:38.80,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the two of you enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.20,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:40.99,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Gorillina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.33,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be the father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.15,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's an actual gorilla there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:46.89,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, her name is Gorillina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.72,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Such an adorable child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.41,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind letting me hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.50,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's a newborn, so her banana hasn't been peeled yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.06,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:59.03,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,My, such an adorable child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.11,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not as adorable as my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:02.95,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:03.99,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:04.46,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Willina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.22,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you raising?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.81,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost more than your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.44,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a wife or husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:16.02,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,I have become the ultimate creature who can be both mother and father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.17,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Have no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.57,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,I will make these children happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.70,Default,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Togoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.73,Default,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Gorillina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.78,Default,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Willina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.70,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.94,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Cut this shit out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.75,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.74,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san was also infected by a wart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.58,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Warts that are attracted to ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.45,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This was one hellish nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.98,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but I learned a valuable lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.61,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The show is finally back on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.69,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stay focused
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.36,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,and aim as high as I can every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.60,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.01,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next week, I'll need to get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.02,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:14.00,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.15,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.76,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're also a wart, Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.64,Default,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:26.53,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:30.16,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone looked different when the show came back on air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.59,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I had a hard time keeping up with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:34.56,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I the only one left out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.10,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Get a clue, you alien warts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:40.72,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate, it's going to get messy when we catch up to the manga and go on another break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.99,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,These people are actually going to train themselves next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.23,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.39,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.41,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:52.38,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[The End]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:28.17,Default,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Next Episode]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:23.32,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a little late for New Year cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:26.95,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And why did everyone send one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.17,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:29.46,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:31.93,Default,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[Use a Calligraphy Pen for New Year Cards]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.22,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Use a calligraphy pen for New Year cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.43,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Plus another one that's a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.89,Default,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}[The Heart Comes Before Chocolate]
